      <tr>
        <td class="Info_Question">
          Yini inhloso yalesi saziso?
        </td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td class="Info_Answer">
          Ukukwazisa ngenani eliklanyelwe isakhiwo sakho nguMasipala walifaka emqulwini omusha wohla lwamanani oqala ukusebenza mhla lulunye (1) kuJulayi 2012.
        </td>
      </tr>

      <tr>
        <td class="Info_Question">
          Kumele ngenzeni?
        </td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td class="Info_Answer">
          Uma wenelisekile ngokuthi leli nani yilo umuzi wakho obungadayiswa ngalo mhla lulunye (1) kuJulayi 2011, akudingekile ukuba kube khona okwenzayo.
          <br></br><br></br>
          Uma kodwa ubona ukuthi leli nani lingaphezulu noma lingaphansi kwenani lomuzi wakho, ungafaka isaziso sokuphikisana nenani elinqunyiwe.
          <br></br><br></br>
          Lokhu ungakwenza ngokugcwalisa ulethe ifomu eyenzelwe lokhu ihambisane nanoma yiluphi ulwazi olweseka ukuphikisa kwakho.
          <br></br><br></br>
          Lama fomu atholakala kuleli kheli elilandelayo: Valuation Roll, Real Estate Unit, 13th Floor, 75 Winder Street, eThekwini.  Ayatholakala nasezikhungweni zezifunda zikaMasipala noma kwi-web ekhelini elithi:  <a class="Link49" href="http://www.durban.gov.za">http://www.durban.gov.za</a>
          <br></br><br></br>
          Amafomu asegcwalisiwe kumele abuyiselwe kuleli kheli elilandelayo:  The Municipal Manager, eThekwini Municipality, Valuation Roll, 13th Floor, 75 Winder Street, Durban ungakadluli umhla wama-31 kuMashi  2012.  Amafomu asegcwalisiwe angathunyelwa nakuleli kheli le e-mail: <a class="Link49"  href="mailto:MundieV@durban.gov.za">MundieV@durban.gov.za</a>.

        </td>
      </tr>

      <tr>
        <td class="Info_Question">
          Ngingakutholaphi ukuthi ezinye izakhiwo ziklanyelwe kumaphi amanani?
        </td>
      </tr>

      <tr>
        <td class="Info_Answer">
          Ungabuka umqulu wohla lwamanani ehhovisi leMenenja kaMasipala, Valuation Roll, 13th Floor, 75 Winder Street, eThekwini, emahhovisi kaMasipala ezifundeni ezehlukahlukene noma kwi-web ethi:  <a class="Link49" href="http://www.durban.gov.za"> www.durban.gov.za</a>
        </td>
      </tr>

      <tr>
            <td class="Info_Question">
              Kuyokwenzekani ngemuva kokuba sengifake ukuphikisa kwami?
            </td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td class="Info_Answer">
              Udaba luyobuyiselwa emuva kumklami wamanani oyobe eselubuka kabusha nalolo lwazi olwengeziwe olunikezile.  Uyobhalelwa waziswe ngomphumela walokho kubuka kabusha.
            </td>
          </tr>

          <tr>
            <td class="Info_Question">
              Kuyokwenzekani uma nangemuva kwalokho ngingakagculiseki ngenani eliklanyelwe umuzi wami?
            </td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td class="Info_Answer">
              Ungafaka isicelo sokwedlulisa udaba lwakho phambili.  Kulesi sigaba udaba lwakho luyocutshungulwa yibhodi emiselwe ukwenza lo msebenzi eqokwa nguHulumeni wesiFundazwe.
            </td>
          </tr>
      
          <tr>
            <td class="Info_Question">
              Sifakwa kanjani isicelo sokwedlulisela phambili isikhalo sami?
            </td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td class="Info_Answer">
              Imininingwane yalokhu uyoyinikezwa kanye nomphumela wokucutsungulwa kokuphikisana kwakho nenani eliklanyiwe.
            </td>
          </tr>


